---
title: Double Sichuan Chicken & Pumpkin Salad with Crushed Peanuts
description: Sichuan garlic paste has got to be our new favourite flavour. This salad is bursting with deliciousness, from the punchy Sichuan chicken to the sweet roast pumpkin. All tied together with a soy dressing and a crushed peanut garnish, this is not a salad that will leave you wanting!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cf027a287a303a0f264034-448fa9a0.jpeg
